00/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe text-secondary/60 self-center\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><button class=\"text-[10px] font-bold transition-all hover:text-white text-secondary text-glow\">EN</button><span class=\"text-white/10 text-[10px]\">|</span><button class=\"text-[10px] font-bold transition-all hover:text-white text-slate-400\">RU</button></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 cyber-grid pointer-events-none opacity-10\"></div><div class=\"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-center\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6 md:gap-8 max-w-2xl\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold border-l-2 border-secondary pl-3 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,182,212,0.3)] bg-black/40 py-1 pr-4 w-fit\">Cyber-Samurai Marketing</div><h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.85] text-white tracking-tighter drop-shadow-2xl\"><span class=\"\">BanzAI<!-- --> </span><span class=\"text-secondary brightness-125\">Marketing:<!-- --> </span><span class=\"\">Your<!-- --> </span><span class=\"text-secondary brightness-125\">Business&#x27;s<!-- --> </span><span class=\"\">Digital<!-- --> </span><span class=\"text-secondary brightness-125\">Katana.<!-- --> </span></h1><div class=\"space-y-4 md:space-y-6 max-w-xl\"><div class=\"border-l border-primary/30 pl-4 md:pl-6 ml-1 group hover:border-secondary transition-colors text-balance\"><p class=\"text-white/95 text-base md:text-xl font-bold mb-1 tracking-tight\">Your marketing department on full autopilot.</p><p class=\"text-white/50 text-[10px] md:text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed uppercase tracking-widest font-medium\">We replace a staff of expensive specialists with a single autonomous system that works 24/7 without holidays or weekends.</p></div><div class=\"border-l border-primary/30 pl-4 md:pl-6 ml-1 group hover:border-secondary transition-colors text-balance\"><p class=\"text-white/95 text-base md:text-xl font-bold mb-1 tracking-tight\">Leads 40% cheaper than the market.</p><p class=\"text-white/50 text-[10px] md:text-xs lg:text-sm leading-relaxed uppercase tracking-widest font-medium\">Due to the ultra-high quality of AI content, ad network algorithms reduce the cost of each impression for you.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-3 md:gap-5 mt-4\"><button class=\"group flex items-center justify-center bg-secondary hover:bg-cyan-400 text-black font-black text-xs md:text-base px-6 py-3 md:px-12 md:py-5 rounded-none transition-all uppercase tracking-wider sharp-border shadow-neon-glow\"><span class=\"mr-2\">UNLEASH THE SWORD</span><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right md:w-5 md:h-5 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"flex items-center justify-center border border-white/20 hover:border-white/40 text-white hover:bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md font-bold text-xs md:text-base px-6 py-3 md:px-10 md:py-5 \">VIEW SHOWREEL</button></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative bg-black flex flex-col items-center overflow-hidden pt-10 pb-20 lg:pt-16 lg:pb-32 px-6\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-red-950/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full flex flex-col items-center gap-16 relative z-10\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter text-center leading-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\">Why are you paying $100 per click?</h2><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center my-12\"><div class=\"absolute w-64 h-64 bg-red-600/30 rounded-full blur-[140px] pointer-events-none\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:none\"></div><div class=\"text-[140px] md:text-[280px] font-black text-white leading-none tracking-tighter animate-pulse-red select-none\" style=\"transform:none\">$100</div></div><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-1 gap-10 w-full\"><div class=\"p-8 border-l-2 border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2 text-white\">Your content is &#x27;invisible&#x27; to algorithms.</p><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wide\">Boring creatives have low CTR. Ad platforms penalize you for this by raising the auction entry price. You pay for your contractors&#x27; boredom.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 border-l-2 border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(20px)\"><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2 text-white\">Critical volume deficit.</p><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wide\">One post a week is hara-kiri. While you&#x27;re stalling, your competitors&#x27; neural networks are already generating 50 tests a day, finding combinations 10x cheaper than yours.</p></div><div class=\"p-8 border-l-2 border-red-600 bg-red-950/10 backdrop-blur-md\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2 text-red-500 glitch\">Zuckerberg&#x27;s yacht won&#x27;t buy itself.</p><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wide\">Without AI optimization, you&#x27;re simply gifting ad giants up to 60% of your budget on ineffective impressions. Stop sponsoring someone else&#x27;s luxury.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"absolute left-0 top-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-red-600/30 to-transparent opacity-50\"></div><div class=\"absolute right-0 top-0 w-1 h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-red-600/30 to-transparent opacity-50\"></div></section><section class=\"relative py-32 px-6 bg-dubai-night border-y border-primary/20 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 cyber-grid opacity-10 pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-[1280px] mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center relative z-10\"><div class=\"relative aspect-square w-full max-w-[280px] sm:max-w-sm md:max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 order-2 lg:order-1 group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-[-10%] rounded-full blur-3xl transition-colors duration-1000 bg-primary/20\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 rounded-full overflow-hidden border border-white/10 z-10 bg-black\"><div class=\"w-full h-full relative\" style=\"opacity:0;filter:brightness(0.2) grayscale(100%);transform:scale(1.1)\"><img alt=\"Founder\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fsher-profile.webp&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-4 md:-inset-6 border-2 border-dashed rounded-full pointer-events-none z-30 opacity-70\"></div><div class=\"absolute -inset-8 md:-inset-12 border border-dotted rounded-full pointer-events-none z-10\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-8 md:-bottom-12 left-1/2 w-max max-w-full -translate-x-1/2 flex flex-col items-center\"><div class=\"font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] md:tracking-[0.4em] px-4 py-1 border-l-2 text-primary border-primary bg-primary/10\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(-5px)\">IDENTITY REVEALED // SHIFT_REALITY_PROTOCOL_ACTIVE</div></div><div class=\"absolute top-0 left-0 w-4 h-4 border-t-2 border-l-2 border-white/40 pointer-events-none z-40\"></div><div class=\"absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-4 h-4 border-b-2 border-r-2 border-white/40 pointer-events-none z-40\"></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-10 order-1 lg:order-2 z-20\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-[0.9]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">System Architect: Sher.</h2><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-12 h-[1px] transition-all duration-1000 bg-primary group-hover:w-16\"></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white/90 uppercase tracking-tight\">Real Dubai market expert since 2015.</p></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wider pl-16\">Built several successful businesses and created Sherlock Cars Dubai by combining local market knowledge with AI systems.</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-12 h-[1px] transition-all duration-1000 bg-primary group-hover:w-16\"></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white/90 uppercase tracking-tight\">Sherlock Cars Dubai Case (2025).</p></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wider pl-16\">Achieved a 130% increase in sales and a 300% increase in reach through complete AI automation of content systems.</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-3\"><div class=\"w-12 h-[1px] transition-all duration-1000 bg-primary group-hover:w-16\"></div><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-white/90 uppercase tracking-tight\">100% AI Generation (0 shoots per year).</p></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm md:text-base leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-wider pl-16\">For the entire year, not a single &quot;live&quot; video was shot — all lead-generating content was entirely generated by neural networks.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex gap-8\"><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-primary font-mono uppercase\">Verified_Experience</span><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">10+ YRS</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-secondary font-mono uppercase\">Market_Presence</span><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">UAE / GLOBAL</span></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative py-32 px-6 bg-black overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"max-w-[1280px] mx-auto relative z-10\"><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-8 mb-24\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter max-w-2xl leading-[0.9]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-30px)\">Minimum of your time — maximum market capture.</h2><div class=\"h-[2px] flex-grow bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/50 to-transparent hidden md:block mb-4\"></div></div><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"relative p-10 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl group hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary/40 transition-colors text-6xl font-black\">0<!-- -->1</div><div class=\"relative z-10 space-y-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-none border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.2)]\">STEP_0<!-- -->1</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter\">Deep Scan.</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-l border-white/10 pl-4\">We find your competitors&#x27; vulnerabilities and the cheapest traffic points. You don&#x27;t need to be an expert — we do it all for you.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-primary/5 to-transparent h-1 opacity-0 group-hover:animate-scanline\"></div></div><div class=\"relative p-10 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl group hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary/40 transition-colors text-6xl font-black\">0<!-- -->2</div><div class=\"relative z-10 space-y-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-none border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.2)]\">STEP_0<!-- -->2</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter\">Neural Deployment.</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-l border-white/10 pl-4\">Launching your personal &#x27;Neural Conveyor&#x27;. The system starts generating leads 24/7.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-primary/5 to-transparent h-1 opacity-0 group-hover:animate-scanline\"></div></div><div class=\"relative p-10 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] backdrop-blur-xl group hover:border-primary/50 transition-all duration-500\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 font-mono text-primary/20 group-hover:text-primary/40 transition-colors text-6xl font-black\">0<!-- -->3</div><div class=\"relative z-10 space-y-6\"><div class=\"w-12 h-12 rounded-none border border-primary/30 flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(168,85,247,0.2)]\">STEP_0<!-- -->3</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter\">Market Expansion.</h3><p class=\"text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed font-medium uppercase tracking-widest border-l border-white/10 pl-4\">Lead cost drops by 40%, sales grow. You simply track the results via the dashboard.</p></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-primary/5 to-transparent h-1 opacity-0 group-hover:animate-scanline\"></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-20 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-10 p-6 border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]\"><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-center\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse shadow-[0_0_8px_#22c55e]\"></div><span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">Network_Status_Optimal</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-center\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">Estimated_ROI_Increase</span><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-secondary text-glow\">+130%</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-center\"><span class=\"text-[10px] text-white/40 font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.3em]\">Lead_Cost_Reduction</span><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-primary text-glow\">-40%</span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"relative py-32 px-6 bg-dubai-night/50 border-y border-secondary/10 overflow-hidden\"><